	<li><a href="http://qz.com/492506/japan-has-scrapped-its-2020-olympics-logo-amid-allegations-of-plagiarism/">Japan Has Scrapped Its 2020 Olympics Logo Amid Allegations of Plagiarism</a></li>&#13;
	<li><a href="http://qz.com/492473/ordinary-citizens-across-europe-are-stepping-in-to-help-refugees-where-their-governments-have-failed/">Ordinary Citizens Across Europe Are Stepping in to Help Refugees Where Their Governments Have Failed</a></li>&#13;
</ul><hr></aside>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <a class="read-more" href="/international/archive/2015/09/china-stock-market-crash/403273/" data-omni-click="inherit">
        
